T09.question: What museums were involved in the IntARSI project?
T09.sparql:
SELECT ?museums, ?museums_labels
WHERE {
  ?papers rdf:type orkgc:Paper.
  ?papers rdfs:label ?papers_labels.
  FILTER(REGEX(?papers_labels, "IntARSI"))
  ?papers orkgp:P31 ?contrib.
  ?contrib orkgp:P41242 ?museums.
  ?museums rdfs:label ?museums_labels.
}

T011.question: What is the most common type of biosensor?
T011.sparql:
SELECT ?biosensor
WHERE {
  orkgr:R151435 orkgp:compareContribution ?contrib.
  ?contrib orkgp:P43095 ?biosensor.
}
ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?biosensor))
LIMIT 1

T014.question: Which energy system modeling papers indicate where to find their simulation software?
T014.sparql:
SELECT ?repo
WHERE {
  ?paper a orkgc:Paper.
  ?paper orkgp:P31 ?contrib.
  ?contrib orkgp:P37586 ?model.
  ?model orkgp:P39010 ?code.
  ?code orkgp:P4077 ?repo.
}

T017.question: When MedPost model was published?
T017.sparql:
SELECT ?year
WHERE {
  ?papers rdf:type orkgc:Paper.

}

T018.question: Which sector is the most commonly modeled energy sector?
T018.sparql:
SELECT ?label (COUNT(?label) AS ?number)
WHERE {
  ?sector rdfs:label ?label;
          a ?class.
  ?class owl:equivalentClass <http://openenergy-platform.org/ontology/oeo/OEO_00000367>.
  orkgr:R150337 orkgp:compareContribution ?contrib.
  ?contrib orkgp:P37586 ?scenario.
  ?scenario orkgp:P37675 ?study.
  ?study orkgp:P37668 ?sector.
  
}
ORDER BY DESC(?number)
LIMIT 1
